    ðŸ”¥ POLICY PAGE DETECTED - GLASS EFFECT SHOULD BE VISIBLE ðŸ”¥<br>
    Policy: {{ page.title }} | URL: {{ page.url }}
  </div>
{%- endif -%}

<!-- DEBUG: Super aggressive debugging -->
<div style="background: orange; color: black; padding: 20px; margin: 20px; font-size: 16px; text-align: left; border: 3px solid red;">
  ðŸ”¥ AGGRESSIVE DEBUG ðŸ”¥<br><br>
  
  <strong>1. PAGE INFO:</strong><br>
  Current URL: <span style="background: yellow;">{{ page.url }}</span><br>
  Page Title: <span style="background: yellow;">{{ page.title }}</span><br>
  Page Handle: <span style="background: yellow;">{{ page.handle }}</span><br>
  Page ID: <span style="background: yellow;">{{ page.id }}</span><br><br>
  
  <strong>2. METHOD TESTING:</strong><br>
  Method 1 (Direct): <span style="background: yellow;">{{ page.url }} == policy.url</span><br>
  Method 2 (Contains): <span style="background: yellow;">{{ page.url contains '/policies/' }}</span><br>
  Method 3 (Title): <span style="background: yellow;">{{ policy_titles }}</span><br>
  Final Result: <span style="background: yellow;">{{ is_policy_page }}</span><br><br>
  
  <strong>3. ALL SHOP POLICIES:</strong><br>
  {% for policy in shop.policies %}
    {%- if policy != blank -%}
      â†’ Policy: <strong>{{ policy.title }}</strong><br>
      â†’ URL: <span style="background: yellow;">{{ policy.url }}</span><br>
      â†’ Handle: <span style="background: yellow;">{{ policy.handle }}</span><br>
      â†’ ID: <span style="background: yellow;">{{ policy.id }}</span><br>
      â†’ Matches?: <span style="background: {% if policy.url == page.url %}green{% else %}red{% endif %};">{{ policy.url == page.url }}</span><br><br>
    {%- endif -%}
  {% endfor %}
  
  <strong>4. MANUAL TESTS:</strong><br>
  Current URL length: {{ page.url.size }}<br>
  URL starts with '/policies': {{ page.url | slice: 0, 9 }}<br>
  Last 20 chars: {{ page.url | slice: -20, 20 }}
